{"tid":1316841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屋企人係和理非佢話今晚","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:58:08.000Z","uid":8105,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71fd955c86ffc2fedb893d6085a420f8c48218bd","tid":1316841,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"d黑警抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屋企人不嬲都係和理非之前2014年嗰時都話好多人收咗錢好多鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知頭先喺度睇直播<br />\n對住個電視機大叫大力啲打力啲<br />\n打死啲差佬就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話手指斷咗個黑警抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween我媽之前港豚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但反送中之後醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收工仲去包圍警察總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad8c6f77dd6465863d27d079b4e6e44ffb94309","tid":1316841,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026267d8956c48049c8583da20a82984b1d8cb37","tid":1316841,"uid":92859,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"［請廣傳］多名正義市民合力制服冒警暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316660</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbWW4fG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbWW4fG.png&h=8ba80528&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d90d70a5c8175104d876b6758482c14f0dc2efd2","tid":1316841,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"今日冇警